  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span>Paper小AI</span> <span>2026-03-19 12:06</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">湖北</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1e56b65b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F12P3TZE7WmR73yF8Zse01YU1qz4HVXNxDsxWoze7jyia8oK5WUn8SyAia6bkaHtmcFIqljQCURHibQd1jXQKBGS0vph3twybxvacSILGLNQJlE%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-family: Optima, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, PingFangSC-regular, serif;letter-spacing: 0.6px;text-align: left;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">嗨，我是PaperAGI，主要关注LLM、RAG、Agent等AI前沿技术，每天分享业界最新成果和实战案例。</span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"PaperAGI\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/r8c4hf2wliabcicsicsLYWwX2Jmd64GLUouRqQBtnvsVklbhnLdbHQickh1WsxoliadiaDFqYyZlATYhDLibc02VL9bWg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"专注DeepResearch／RAG／Graph / Agent前沿技术与企业落地！每天分享新方案，新方法。\" data-id=\"Mzk0NTcyNTMzNw==\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"0\"></mp-common-profile></span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;padding: 8px 0px;font-family: Optima, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, PingFangSC-light, serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">基于知识图谱（Knowledge Graph, KG）的检索增强生成（RAG）在问答任务中面临一个核心难题：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bold;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(69, 190, 217);background: none left top / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);width: auto;height: auto;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border-style: none;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-radius: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">三元组索引会丢失上下文语义</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。当文本被压缩为（头实体-关系-尾实体）三元组时，很多隐含的背景信息被剥离，导致多跳推理（Multi-hop QA）性能大打折扣。多跳问答需要从多个实体、事实或关系中组合答案，对上下文理解要求极高，传统方法的语义丢失问题在此类任务中尤为突出。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 30px 0px 15px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);font-weight: 500;cursor: pointer;align-items: unset;background: none 0% 0% / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255);border-style: none;border-width: 1px;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);border-radius: 0px;box-shadow: none;display: flex;flex-direction: unset;float: unset;height: auto;justify-content: center;line-height: 1.5em;overflow: unset;padding: 0px;text-align: left;text-shadow: none;transform: none;width: auto;-webkit-box-reflect: unset;font-family: Optima, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, PingFangSC-light, serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;cursor: pointer;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0em;margin: 0px;padding: 0px 10px 0px 0px;align-items: unset;background: linear-gradient(0deg, rgb(231, 247, 252) 40%, transparent 40%) 0% 0% / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box transparent;border-style: none;border-width: 1px;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);border-radius: 0px;box-shadow: none;color: rgb(112, 188, 234);content: unset;display: block;font-weight: bold;font-style: normal;flex-direction: unset;float: unset;height: auto;justify-content: unset;overflow: unset;text-align: left;text-indent: 0em;text-shadow: none;transform: none;width: auto;-webkit-box-reflect: unset;\"><span leaf=\"\">MDER-DR 双阶段框架</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;padding: 8px 0px;font-family: Optima, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, PingFangSC-light, serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者提出了一个</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bold;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(69, 190, 217);background: none left top / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);width: auto;height: auto;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border-style: none;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-radius: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">领域无关的 KG-QA 框架</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，覆盖索引和检索推理两个阶段，由两个核心组件协同工作：</span></p>\n  <figure style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 10px 0px;cursor: pointer;padding: 0px;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: center;align-items: center;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Optima, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, PingFangSC-light, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n   <span 