Hop Question Answering with Entity-Centric Summaries</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2603.11223\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/pdf/2603.11223</a></span></code></pre>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-family: Optima, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, PingFangSC-regular, serif;letter-spacing: 0.6px;text-align: left;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">每天一篇大模型Paper来锻炼我们的思维~已经读到这了，别忘了点赞、关注噢</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-family: Optima, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, PingFangSC-regular, serif;letter-spacing: 0.6px;text-align: left;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">推荐阅读</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"3 5 []\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline: 0px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-family: Optima, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, PingFangSC-regular, serif;letter-spacing: 0.6px;text-align: left;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.6;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline: 0px;line-height: 1.6;\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding-right: 0px;padding-left: 0px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);cursor: default;line-height: 1.6;\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk0NTcyNTMzNw==&amp;mid=2247485616&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=8f798e53ccd52dff066897e4c519ce97&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"用“出处”打败幻觉：RAG归因最新研究综述\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" 